cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.HC 

This paper deals with machine learning models and natural language processing techniques to analyze online hotel reviews. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning algorithms, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses the use of XAI methodology, which could place it in cs.IR (Information Retrieval) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper discusses the visualization of the prediction mechanism, which could place it in cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction).
